{"type": "article", "id": 27496, "title": "独立茶室", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-30T07:04:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121356MhFRXEoPxrb7VZd0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你喜欢一个人静静地喝茶，Mimi Jung 设计的这个<a href=\"http://www.mimijung.com/tea-house\">独立茶室</a>是一个不错的选择。除了宗教与文化元素，Jung 富有现代感的诠释进一步强调了安慰以及自省的力量。茶室的圆柱形框架可以通过旋转的方式进行开关，通过半透明的墙壁使人与外部环境隔离。茶室内还配备了一张低矮的木桌，供人饮茶小坐或是进行冥想。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121354oFdcy8CeS50fIYZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121354SWyGogJe9CfjiFPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.721\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121355LTRfCSwKBgxqMZW8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121355EgRNB3lyiofm4WHV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}